description:
There is a rumor among the criminals that the myth, the phantom is back with the skull marks on some of their own men who had encountered the ghost who walks in the Bengali jungle.

While continuing to pursue to know more about Krieghund, Kit flees away from the jungle area while he bumps into a friend, his father's old mate, Guran and his sons who are dedicated to protect the ghost who walks like always.

With the world taking him for dead, Kit, The Phantom in true sense, now gears up with guns, ammo and the invisible suit acquired from one of the mercenaries. He tracks war mongers to their den in South Africa.
